843
01:01:44,260 --> 01:01:46,730
That's how I feel.

844
01:01:46,730 --> 01:01:48,950
If only Jong Hui makes up her mind,

845
01:01:48,950 --> 01:01:53,900
Jullee is confident we can give her
the fullest support and care.

846
01:01:53,900 --> 01:01:57,410
- What do you think?
- Gosh, I'm not sure.

847
01:01:57,410 --> 01:02:00,430
Miss Korea was a vague dream of mine as a child.

848
01:02:00,430 --> 01:02:02,710
- Oh, my!
- We're not interested.

849
01:02:03,680 --> 01:02:06,320
She's going to inherit the family business.

850
01:02:06,320 --> 01:02:09,670
We don't have time to waste
on things like Miss Korea.

851
01:02:09,670 --> 01:02:13,080
We're looking into studying abroad
at George Mason University near D.C.

852
01:02:13,080 --> 01:02:16,760
Miss Korea credentials, how should I say this...

853
01:02:16,760 --> 01:02:22,170
It wouldn't hurt her studies or future career.

854
01:02:22,170 --> 01:02:27,590
How about you, Jong Hui? Do you feel the same?

855
01:02:27,590 --> 01:02:29,960
Yes, well...

856
01:02:29,960 --> 01:02:33,070
If my mom doesn't want it, then I'm also...

857
01:02:33,070 --> 01:02:35,040
I see.

858
01:02:36,600 --> 01:02:38,310
Understood.

859
01:02:38,310 --> 01:02:41,730
I thought I'd try to make a pitch just in case.

860
01:02:41,730 --> 01:02:43,730
But I was dreaming too big.

861
01:02:43,730 --> 01:02:46,960
I'll back down with no regrets.

862
01:02:46,960 --> 01:02:49,800
Please dig in. Dig in.

863
01:02:50,720 --> 01:02:52,220
Let's eat.

864
01:03:00,930 --> 01:03:03,610
I was told that the stylist was fired.

865
01:03:03,610 --> 01:03:05,300
Of course, Chairwoman.

866
01:03:05,300 --> 01:03:08,010
She was terminated that very day.

867
01:03:08,010 --> 01:03:12,070
If nothing else, I have a good
sense for those things.

868
01:03:12,070 --> 01:03:14,080
A mistake is a mistake,

869
01:03:14,080 --> 01:03:17,130
