872
01:03:24,550 --> 01:03:26,500
Did you enjoy the meal?

873
01:03:26,500 --> 01:03:28,330
Yes, it was good.

874
01:03:32,870 --> 01:03:35,060
Why did you do that?

875
01:03:35,060 --> 01:03:38,020
Was it because you knew
she was my friend? Is that it?

876
01:03:38,020 --> 01:03:39,680
Lower your voice.

877
01:03:39,680 --> 01:03:41,680
How could you raise your voice so vulgarly?

878
01:03:41,680 --> 01:03:44,560
Mom, her livelihood depends on that job.

879
01:03:44,560 --> 01:03:45,920
Even if she made a mistake, how-

880
01:03:45,920 --> 01:03:49,350
You shouldn't have ignored what I said!

881
01:03:49,351 --> 01:04:09,339
Officail Website : kissasian.be

882
01:04:09,363 --> 01:04:29,351
Translate by =Qari= @Team Viki

883
01:03:49,350 --> 01:03:51,330
Mom.

884
01:03:51,330 --> 01:03:52,820
