895
01:04:27,490 --> 01:04:29,400
Where do you think you're going?

896
01:04:30,370 --> 01:04:32,110
Jong Hui.

897
01:04:43,910 --> 01:04:46,380
Oppa, thank you so much!

898
01:04:46,380 --> 01:04:48,510
I'll treat you next time! I'm late.

899
01:04:48,510 --> 01:04:50,470
- Drive safe!
- Sure.

900
01:04:54,000 --> 01:04:56,400
