941
01:09:26,680 --> 01:09:30,840
Ms. K from Dodam-dong writes...

942
01:09:30,840 --> 01:09:33,070
Giant.

943
01:09:33,070 --> 01:09:39,340
My first meeting with him is remembered as Giant.

944
01:09:39,340 --> 01:09:44,220
As always, I was calling out "All right!"
