951
01:10:07,200 --> 01:10:11,340
Yet I couldn't turn away from our connection.

952
01:10:11,340 --> 01:10:13,900
Because he was my first love.

953
01:10:15,680 --> 01:10:22,820
And even now, he remains by my side like a Giant.

954
